properties.Name: CommissionSchedule
properties.Description: A schedule or published list of parameters by which commissions are calculated under various scenarios or conditions.

Columns.Name: CommissionScheduleId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Commission Schedule.

Columns.Name: CommissionScheduleEffectiveStartDate
Columns.Description: The effective start date or first date that the Commission Schedule is in effect.

Columns.Name: CommissionScheduleEffectiveEndDate
Columns.Description: The effective end date or last date that the Commission Schedule is in effect.

Columns.Name: CommissionScheduleName
Columns.Description: The name of the Commission Schedule.

Columns.Name: CommissionScheduleDescription
Columns.Description: A description of the Commission Schedule.

Columns.Name: CommissionScheduleEligibilityStatement
Columns.Description: A statement of the eligibility of an employee or third party to be assigned commissions using the associated Commission Schedule.

Columns.Name: CommissionScheduleRestrictionsStatement
Columns.Description: A statement detailing the restrictions that are applied to the associated Commission Schedule.

Columns.Name: CommissionScheduleTypeId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Commission Schedule Type.
